---
// Discography page (EN): album overview and main streaming links.
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AlbumStreamingStatus from '../../components/AlbumStreamingStatus.astro';

// Optional listening links, configured via public environment variables.
const YOUTUBE_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_KILLBIRGAHN_YOUTUBE_URL as string | undefined;
const SOUNDCLOUD_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_KILLBIRGAHN_SOUNDCLOUD_URL as string | undefined;
const DEEZER_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_KILLBIRGAHN_DEEZER_URL as string | undefined;

const streamingLinks = [
  { label: 'YouTube', url: YOUTUBE_URL, iconClass: 'fa-brands fa-youtube' },
  { label: 'SoundCloud', url: SOUNDCLOUD_URL, iconClass: 'fa-brands fa-soundcloud' },
  { label: 'Deezer', url: DEEZER_URL, iconClass: 'fa-brands fa-deezer' },
].filter((link) => Boolean(link.url && link.url.startsWith('http')));

const siteUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_URL ?? 'https://granitmitoyen.com';

const albumSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'MusicAlbum',
  name: 'Lands Of Killbirgahn',
  byArtist: {
    '@type': 'MusicGroup',
    name: 'Granit Mitoyen',
  },
  genre: 'Stoner Metal',
  inLanguage: 'en',
  url: new URL(Astro.url.pathname, siteUrl).toString(),
  track: [
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 1, name: 'Asel' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 2, name: '20 Days of Night' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 3, name: 'The Journey' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 4, name: 'Samael' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 5, name: 'Fire Rain' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 6, name: 'Psychedelic Dream' },
    { '@type': 'MusicRecording', position: 7, name: 'Heavy Wolf' },
  ],
  sameAs: [YOUTUBE_URL, SOUNDCLOUD_URL, DEEZER_URL].filter(
    (url): url is string => Boolean(url && url.startsWith('http'))
  ),
};

const structuredData = [albumSchema];

const pageTitle = 'Discography';
const pageDescription =
  'Lands Of Killbirgahn, a dark fantasy concept album by Granit Mitoyen: a brutal story with no heroes, between ice, night and fire.';
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} structuredData={structuredData}>
  <h1 class="font-title text-dark text-3xl font-bold mb-6 title-underline inline-block">
    {pageTitle}
  </h1>

  <section class="mb-10 space-y-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-2xl font-semibold">
        Lands Of Killbirgahn
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Killbirgahn is a dark fantasy concept album where ice, night and fire mark the downfall of
        a doomed world. Divine manipulation, human mistakes and ancient forces collide in a brutal
        story with no heroes and no redemption. Balance is only ever restored through destruction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <AlbumStreamingStatus
      imageSrc="/images/Granit Mitoyen - Lands Of Killbirgahn cover.jpg"
      imageAlt="Lands Of Killbirgahn – album cover"
      availableTitle="Listen to the album"
      unavailableTitle='Album "Lands of Killbirghan" coming soon!'
    />
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-6 max-w-3xl">
    <h2 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 title-underline inline-block">
      Track-by-track story
    </h2>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        Asel
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Out on the ice, Asel hears voices as the light fades away. Night settles in, and her fate
        closes on her with no escape.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        20 Days of Night
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Twenty days without sunlight plunge Asel into a frozen wandering. The dead rise, her mind
        fractures, and humanity slowly disappears in the dark.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        The Journey
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Brought back from the dead, Asel is forced to march toward war. A slave to gods and hell,
        there is no way back for her anymore.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        Samael
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Alone and terrified, a young apprentice mage faces a threat he cannot understand. Fear
        drives him to make a mistake that cannot be undone.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        Fire Rain
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        A forbidden spell is cast. The sky burns, the world catches fire, and the apocalypse is set
        in motion.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        Psychedelic Dream
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        Fleeing the real world, the narrator hides in a psychedelic delirium where dream and
        reality merge. Power and destruction become a distorted mirror of society&apos;s flaws.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="font-subtitle text-dark text-xl font-semibold">
        Heavy Wolf
      </h3>
      <p class="font-body text-dark leading-relaxed">
        When gods and mortals both fail, an ancient force awakens. The Heavy Wolf restores order by
        sheer force, correcting a world that has gone too far.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>

